From Paul Andresen Subject Re Braves Pitching UpdateDIR In article Sherri Nichols writes In article writes This certainly passes the common sense test for me but is there any statistical evidence to say what percent of defense is pitching and what percent is fielding Not yet I wish there It's much more difficult to tease these apart than to tease apart scoring runs and preventing And thus we come to one of the true beauties of baseball these things along with many others will never be Almost everything in baseball is situational and This is what allows us to carry on all the arguments that we If everything could be explained and balanced on a statistical basis none of the wonder and mystery would be Why we might have to resort to just going out the ballyard and enjoy the game Paul feeling a little anti stathead today We will stretch no farm animal beyond its natural length Paul Andresen Hewlett Packard home NW McKinley Corvallis OR A SABR member since